column5: Woah there. Calm down. I simply asked a question. I did not say you were lying.
2500 is very specific. Do you have a source?

Man it makes me cringe. Watching people on social media talking to each other like they were alone.

GET A FUCKING ROOM!
Hey:)! I recommend writing it down before you talk to your therapist.

Do it. Please for the love of god do it. I do it, all my friends do it, the people who say they do not do it actually do it. Everyone has hair growing between their eyebrows, not plucking them looks stupid.
Dont ask people on the internett to be your doctor... bad idea mate.
